The '''High Elders''' were traditionally the highest-ranking priests in the [[High Circle of Elders]] on [[Monastery/Legends|Monastery]]. Their authority was briefly usurped by [[Domina Tagge/Legends|Domina Tagge]], who was voted to the new rank of [[All-High Priestess]] when the Circle was mentally influenced by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]].

